    <div class="section">
      

<div id="review_1791172639" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/1791172639" />
    <a title="Hákon Gunnarsson" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/20498454-h-kon-gunnarsson"><img alt="Hákon Gunnarsson" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1474574814p2/20498454.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/1791172639?book_show_action=true">Oct 22, 2016</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Hákon Gunnarsson" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Hákon Gunnarsson" href="/user/show/20498454-h-kon-gunnarsson">Hákon Gunnarsson</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Audiobook 9780140861082" href="/book/show/811829.The_Old_Patagonian_Express">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/20498454-h-kon-gunnarsson?shelf=non-fiction">non-fiction</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/20498454-h-kon-gunnarsson?shelf=audiobook">audiobook</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/20498454-h-kon-gunnarsson?shelf=travel">travel</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1791172639" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer16028140882863221344">There are parts in this book which I find brilliant, funny, entertaining, and even deep. A description of reading Lovecraft on a train full of people that probably thought the name referred to something naughty is quite good for example. <br/><br/>It&apos;s just a little too much of this book. I think I might have liked it more in shorter form because in the end it was starting to feel like challenge to finish. Maybe it was just too long a trip for the book. Or maybe I didn&apos;t feel like going all this way with </span>
  <span id="freeText16028140882863221344" style="display:none">There are parts in this book which I find brilliant, funny, entertaining, and even deep. A description of reading Lovecraft on a train full of people that probably thought the name referred to something naughty is quite good for example. <br /><br />It's just a little too much of this book. I think I might have liked it more in shorter form because in the end it was starting to feel like challenge to finish. Maybe it was just too long a trip for the book. Or maybe I didn't feel like going all this way with Theroux. He is a good writer though. </span>
  <a data-text-id="16028140882863221344" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


