<div id="review_4381664439" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/4381664439" />
    <a title="Wayne Jordaan" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/27429405-wayne-jordaan"><img alt="Wayne Jordaan" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1389089178p2/27429405.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/4381664439?book_show_action=true">Dec 16, 2021</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Wayne Jordaan" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Wayne Jordaan" href="/user/show/27429405-wayne-jordaan">Wayne Jordaan</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Hardcover " href="/book/show/59794047-the-old-patagonian-express">review of another edition</a>


        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer4381664439" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer14183915589997421931">I enjoy Paul Theroux’ writing, and this one, describing his late 1970s journey from Boston to Esquel in Argentina is no exception. I say journey, but more appropriately, it is a series of mostly train journeys down the two Americas, acutely observed and described with wit and candour. Interesting title, but to find out why, I recommend you hop aboard.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


      <div class="reviewFooter uitext buttons">
          

